The evidence with the title 'The plan - Pickens Plan ' says Depending on OPEC and other foreign sources for half of our oil puts America in a precarious position . In addition to putting our security in the hands of potentially unfriendly and unstable OPEC nations , we are jeopardizing our economy. In 2013 , we imported 1.35 billion barrels of oil from OPEC at a cost of $147 billion. 
